Generate heatmaps

plot_selected_heatmaps <- function(all, column_sets, order_rownames, update_rownames, save_path = NULL) {
  heatmaps <- list()

  for (i in seq_along(all)) {
    if (ncol(all[[i]]) > 70) {
      for (columns in column_sets) {
        if (all(columns %in% colnames(all[[i]]))) {
          data <- all[[i]] %>% select(all_of(columns))
          data <- data[order_rownames, ]
          rownames(data) <- update_rownames
          
          # Replace infinite and NA values with 0
          data[is.infinite(as.matrix(data))] <- 0
          data[is.na(as.matrix(data))] <- 0
          
          rg <- max(abs(as.matrix(data)), na.rm = TRUE)
          heatmap <- pheatmap(
            t(as.matrix(data)), 
            na_col = "grey",  
            main = paste(names(all)[i], paste(columns, collapse = " vs ")),
            breaks = seq(-rg, rg, length.out = 100),
            treeheight_row = 0, treeheight_col = 0,
            cluster_rows = FALSE, cluster_cols = FALSE,
            silent = TRUE,
            gaps_row = 2
          )
          
          heatmaps[[paste0(names(all)[i], "_", paste(columns, collapse = "_"))]] <- heatmap
        }
      }
    }
  }

  # Filter out NULL values
  heatmaps <- Filter(Negate(is.null), heatmaps)

  # Arrange heatmaps in a grid
  grid.arrange(grobs = lapply(heatmaps, function(x) x$gtable), ncol = 2)

  # Save if path provided
  if (!is.null(save_path)) {
    svg(save_path, width = 12, height = 5)
    grid.arrange(grobs = lapply(heatmaps, function(x) x$gtable), ncol = 2)
    dev.off()
  }
}

    data = all[[i]] %>% select(CardiomyocytesAnkrd1pos_Neutrophils, Neutrophils_CardiomyocytesAnkrd1pos)
    data <- data[order_rownames, ]
    # Replace infinite and NA values with 0
    data[is.infinite(as.matrix(data))] <- 0
    data[is.na(as.matrix(data))] <- 0
